    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines an echo function for the connection-less network layer protocol.  The mechanism that is mandated here is in the final process of being standardized by ISO as "Amendment X: Addition of an Echo function to ISO 8473" an integral part of Version 2 of ISO 8473. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
